{"tid":966604,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"補教名師被爆與女學生玩多P還互拍下體片","createTime":"2019-01-03T02:27:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-03T04:23:48.000Z","uid":141892,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d978964e36862742f249517c9ede5bdebd577847","tid":966604,"uid":141892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T02:27:55.000Z","msg":"中國一名女子爆料，「文都考研」的補習班老師在隱瞞引婚的情況，跟多名女學生有不正常的關係，該名被爆料的男老師稱，已經付給爆料女子10萬人民幣(約45萬新台幣)，目前走司法程序解決。<br />\n<br />\n據《北京青年報》報導，網友「起風時333」在《微博》爆料，稱自己是一名補習班的學生，和補習班老師劉一男存在兩性關係，但交往過程中發現劉一男隱瞞自己有家室，與多名女生有染，人數不下30人，還跟女助理視訊的時候互相露下體給對方看，爆料者稱，一次會面時，劉一男把她灌醉後上床，「被你害完以後，被逼做了一個不光榮的角色。」<br />\n<br />\n遭爆料後，劉一男稱自己和爆料的李姓女子確實認識，但與多人淫亂並不屬實，跟爆料者交往時發現對方是對著錢財而來，之後還要巨額分手費。至於爆料者貼出的雙方聊天紀錄，劉一男回應說手機被對方拿走，自行互發後截圖，將跟爆料女子走司法途徑解決此事。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190103/1493781/?utm_campaign=twad_social_appledaily.tw&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190103%2F1493781%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_appledaily.tw%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=s782VIATokQK7aLWwCtuW10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=748a594c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190103%2F1493781%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_appledaily.tw%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=48d48556\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190103/1493781/?utm_campaign=twad_social_appledaily.tw&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"c3e5fbc4fbbc81b35c09c3cd60cf7466f69b5e88","tid":966604,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T02:32:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a7fb6ff4063b12ef50e3dbc71fe0ca6d3863